ked Alice\n   152\t    When the system checks for mutual like\n   153\t    Then 
no match record should exist\n   154\t    And no conversation should be created\
n   155\t```\n   156\t\n   157\t#### 技术要求\n   158\t\n   159\t- 匹配判定：在 
