atch (e) {\n  emit(AuthFailure(e.toString()));\n}\n```\n\nIf the login API faile
d, we should see a SnackBar with the error. But the screenshot shows no SnackBar
.\n\nWait, looking at the screenshot again - the button says "登录" and looks no
rmal. If `AuthAuthenticating` was emitted, `_isLoading` would be true and the bu
